					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-6 font-weight-bold">Interest and maturity</div>
						<div class="col-6 text-right">5% Interest for 12 Months</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-6 font-weight-bold">Uni-level affiliation program</div>
						<div class="col-6 text-right">Included. Valid for 12 Months</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-6 font-weight-bold">Requirement</div>
						<div class="col-6 text-right">1 Valid/Government issued ID</div>
					</div>
					<hr class="separator">
					<div style="font-style: italic">
						The company will entitled you a membership to the uni-level affiliation program valid  for 12 Months (renewable).
					</div>
					<div>
						<button class="btn btn-outline-primary bronze float-right">Apply Now &raquo;</button>
